data.description: This home is truly a gem in the heart of the Wissinoming section of Philadelphia. Its unique feature of being situated on a corner double lot sets it apart from other homes in the area. Not only does it offer extra yard space, but it also provides the convenience of a large deck and an above ground pool, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. As you step inside, you'll immediately feel the warmth and charm of this home. The spacious and inviting interior welcomes you with open arms, making you feel right at home. The main entrance leads you to a parlor room and a formal sitting room, creating the perfect space for entertaining guests. The upgraded flooring throughout the main level adds a touch of elegance and sophistication. Continuing into the dining room and living room, you'll appreciate the seamless flow of the layout. The fully renovated chef's kitchen is a dream come true, offering an eat-in area, a cozy window seat, and even a tastefully integrated laundry area. The attention to detail in the design is evident, making this kitchen both functional and beautiful. Upstairs, you'll discover four generously sized bedrooms, each offering ample space for relaxation and personalization. The primary suite is a true masterpiece, with an abundance of natural light flooding in and a Juliet closet with a balcony overlooking the entire room. The exquisite bathroom is beyond spacious, providing a luxurious retreat within your own home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exquisite home your own. Schedule a showing today and start envisioning the life you could create in this beautiful residence. Whether you're looking for a place to raise a family or a peaceful retreat to call your own, this home has it all. However, with its unique features and desirable location, it's important not to wait too long. Opportunities like this are rare and tend to be snatched up quickly. Don't let this one slip away.
